{"tid":1127150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耀東邨老翁雙料自殺 頂唔順報警","createTime":"2019-04-27T01:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T01:34:37.000Z","uid":3090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db372ffcd8c1e36715bbd658a26aa120692eeb3a","tid":1127150,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XOWcUF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XOWcUF.png&h=cf8748c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自殺老翁送往東區醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣耀東邨耀明樓一單位，昨晚11時許，一名87歲姓丘老翁報案，指自己企圖自殺。警員接報到場，在廚房發現該老翁，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭，調查後相信他曾用刀割頸自殘，清醒被送往東區醫院治理。警方未有撿獲遺書，初步調查沒有可疑，列企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=c95b5412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"a89270529d455595bd4890c7f163526212fc056e","tid":1127150,"uid":62850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687e8108dfadbd505df13ce0d75fbf5b412f298d","tid":1127150,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"係咪睇完張翠山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24632dd2034dcf25c77c76588417cf9395f0b31b","tid":1127150,"ui